10:
Whew, that was close! Glad we
managed to bring it down somehow.
14:
It's no wonder the Guild placed a bounty 
on that monster... 
I'm certain Lilie will be relieved.
18:
We'll take this part as proof.
Finally, I shouldn't have to worry
about money for a little whil—
21:
Hey, you! You better not be walking
off with our loot!
24:
Your what? We brought this thing
down ourselves.
27:
Keep running your mouth and see
what happens. Hand it over!
30: Hey, everybody! Hold up a sec!
33:
Huh? Get lost, brat. You've got
nothing to do with this!
36:
I'm Misogi, not some brat! And you're
wrong anyway!
51:
I can't just get lost when my big
brother's in trouble!
54:
All right, sure. Then tell your brother
he can't go taking other people's
bounties.
56:
Bounty? Dunno what that is, but do
you want money or something?
60:
In that case, you can have the
treasure I just found!
63:
This chest is filled with sparkly gems.
It's perfect for you guys!
66:
Gems from the Kaleidoscope, eh? So
like... elemental gems? Or maybe
something from another world?
68:
...Eh, sure. We'll take your treasure
and see ourselves out, missy.
70:
Heh! Stupid kid doesn't know what
this stuff is worth—
76:
Haha, gotcha! That was a soap
bomb totally stuffed with chili
pepper extract!
82:
Hehe! The soapy water makes
everything slippery, so be careful!
85:
Stupid kid! You're not gonna get
away with messing with us!
92:
Thank you! Finally, I've saved the
best for last...
101:
Nice! We smoked 'em for real this
time!
111:
No need to thank me! Pranking
those goons was a BLAST!
114:
Besides, I'm the sorta girl who can't
ignore someone in need!
117:
...But I'll never turn down an
opportunity for a good prank, either!
122:
Well, the matter of mischief aside...
Are you always taking on the
Kaleidoscope alone?
126:
Kuh...lie...duh-what?
You mean that big maze?
129: By the way... Where even are we?
133:
...Misogi. Where'd you come from?
How did you find yourself in that
maze?
137:
What do you mean? We're in
Landosol. I was digging out a pitfall
in the city, when suddenly
everything around me got all bendy
and squishy...
139:
And then, somehow... I was in that
big maze.
143:
Landosol? Wait... You must know
Pecorine and the others!
147:
Ah! Well, if it isn't my other "big
brother!"
151:
Wait... You two aren't siblings, are
you?
156:
Not exactly, but close enough, I
guess! Right, mister?
160:
Well, at any rate, I'm just glad you've
got some familiar faces to be
around now.
165:
I've already spoken with Pecorine.
She says they'll take care of you at
the Gourmet Guild until you can find
a way home.
170:
Really?! I get to stay with you guys?
Yaaay!
174:
And we're in a different world, too!
It's all just too exciting!
178: Alk, if you've got the time...
183:
Wowww! This is crazy! You're telling
me all those dots out there are other
worlds?!
187:
Are you guys always out there
exploring them?
191:
Well, not ALL of them, but we sure
get a lot of exploring done.
195:
That's so cool! You know, I wanna be
an awesome explorer like my dad
someday!
199:
Hey, Alk! You should take me with
you exploring sometime!
203:
Sure. And I've gotta help you look for
clues to get back to Landosol, too.
208:
You're gonna help?! Wow! Thanks,
Alk!
211:
Okay then! We gotta shake on our
new friendship! Put 'er there!
217: Very well. We look forward to—
226: Ha-HA! Gotcha! It's just a toy, Light!
234:
Haha! Consider that my way of
saying "Nice to meet you!"
